strings: <voice_0x010015A1><se_low>*: Oh, it's you! The fellows from Prince Charmles's initiation ceremony!
<voice_0x010015A2><se_low>*: Don't you remember me? I'm the Chancellor of Argonia! This must be fate! You were meant to find me here!

<voice_0x010015A3><se_low>*: You have to help us!
We'll be a troll's dinner at this rate!
Can't you overpower them?
<voice_0x010015A4><se_low>*: Eh? What you want?

<voice_0x010015A5><se_low>*: We be about to eat!
Maybe you be joining us!
Or is you here to get in the way?

<voice_0x010015A6><se_low>*: Then be gone!
Go now and I don't be eating you!

<voice_0x010015A7><se_low>*: This be a troll kitchen!
You can't be staying here.

<voice_0x010015A8><se_low>*: WHAAAAT!? You is!
Then let's be seeing how strong you be.
We trolls don't be liking tough'uns.

<voice_0x010015A9><se_low>*: Hmmm... You is looking a bit tough.
How about you just leavin' us be?
Too many cooks...
<voice_0x010015AA><se_low>*: You is wanting to eat MY dinner!?
<voice_0x010015AB><se_low>*: NO! You is not having it! No, no, NOOO!
<voice_0x010015AC><se_low>*: You be!? Thank you, thank you!
<voice_0x010015AD><se_low>*: I is healing you because you is so nice.
<voice_0x010015AE><se_low>*: That be all. Now you be gone!
<voice_0x010015AF><se_low>*: Eh? What be it now?
<voice_0x010015B0><se_low>*: Is you...? You IS wanting to eat my dinner!?
<voice_0x010015B1><se_low>*: NO! I is nice to you before, but now you is bad! You is not having it!
<voice_0x010015B2><se_low>*: Let's taste your meat, tough'un!
<voice_0x010015B3><se_low>*: Good! Good! You is as wise as us trolls.
<voice_0x010015B4><se_low>*: Now you be gone!
<voice_0x010015B5><se_low>*: Wha...? If you is not here, I be having a scrumptious dinner now! But I is a troll, so...
<voice_0x010015B6><se_low>*: ...maybe this all be just a dream!
<voice_0x010015B7><se_low>*: Thank you, thank you! If you hadn't come along, I'd have been in a troll's belly by now!

<voice_0x010015B8><se_low>*: What a waste to end up a troll's dinner after all my hard work to become Chancellor
of Argonia!

<voice_0x010015B9><se_low>*: I must repay you for this!
What could I give you...?
<voice_0x010015BA><se_low>*: Of course! Here, I'd like you to have these!
<Cap><leader> obtains 2 seeds of strength and 3 seeds of life.
<voice_0x010015BB><se_low>*: Seeds like that kept me alive in the cell...
<voice_0x010015BC><se_low>*: Well, I should be getting back. Farewell.
